{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a694c61e16","title":"江青观看歌舞演出的讲话记录稿","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a7cd5bcc45","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":24,"articleId":"a694c61e16"}],"tags":[{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"江青，本世纪初国内老左编","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/jqjianghua.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6eb2b6e18f","type":"title","text":"江青观看歌舞演出的讲话记录稿","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"793581b960","type":"authors","text":"江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"b17c7e65ad","type":"paragraph","text":"〖晚，于会泳传达：首长看了这台歌舞节目很高兴，对大家很关心，希望继续加工提高。首长对剧场卫生很注意，不要一抹到处是灰。《阳春白雪》、《春江花月夜》、《渔舟唱晚》都是（首长）点的，整个晚会首长都是兴致勃勃，只是时间紧。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"012d9ee2c3","type":"paragraph","text":"①筝","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"8714824a22","type":"paragraph","text":"弹筝的女同志不敢穿裙子，可以穿褶裙，设计几种，淡绿、淡蓝、银灰色的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"7426fecb9a","type":"paragraph","text":"听工艺展览会的同志讲，东北营口可以造筝、琵琶，你们可去买一点。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"44b7df7da1","type":"paragraph","text":"②看女声弹唱时说：这衣服还不错，可设计几套不同的式样，在不同的季节穿。给她们买一双白色塑料鞋也不算多嘛！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"f945a369ba","type":"paragraph","text":"化妆太难看。眉毛那么短，眼睛像个窟窿。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"627aa194de","type":"paragraph","text":"③舞蹈","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"ed1d724679","type":"paragraph","text":"怎么一看都是少数民族的东西，汉族的为什么不搞？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"c7772f61fb","type":"paragraph","text":"汉族的歌舞也很丰富多彩，应该很好发展，要攻汉族舞，要搞些短小的汉族歌舞。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"5f14e02789","type":"paragraph","text":"《霸王别姬》就可搞成一个很好的剑舞。京剧可说是集汉族歌舞精华之大成。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"5b9081358b","type":"paragraph","text":"《击鼓骂曹》可以搞成一个很好的器乐曲。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"654e8ab83f","type":"paragraph","text":"④舞蹈：送粮","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"a5ee34f444","type":"paragraph","text":"这个舞蹈整个色彩没绿，很单调。椰子树也太小，也不给点光，像个瘪三。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"d2411b5192","type":"paragraph","text":"司机上来穿的裤子绿也不绿，蓝也不蓝，很难看。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"0c33ef079e","type":"paragraph","text":"要很好发展汉族舞蹈，不要都搞少数民族的。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"5f0a815c58","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤二胡","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"dbc58c13a0","type":"paragraph","text":"你看又不敢穿裙子。你们不敢穿我就带头穿。不要把女同志打扮得灰溜溜的。墨绿的、玫瑰红的都可以。褶子可以打在两边，可搞飘带，袖口、领边，可绣些小花。京剧的大包裙，中国不穿，朝鲜还穿。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"290446eeeb","type":"paragraph","text":"《二泉映月》曲子还是好的。但可以动一动，出些新，有些地方云彩遮住月亮，有的地方月亮透过云彩，突出月亮，明亮点。哀怨情绪要表现出来。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"6fe73ca8c8","type":"paragraph","text":"③朱××的裙子很难看，又短，至少可加长二寸，设计白色的，你们不敢穿，我带头穿。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"5e420c894d","type":"paragraph","text":"（第二首歌时）你看，又是少数民族的。男子服装，领口不一定都扣得那么紧。可以设计开领的。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"97d70288d8","type":"paragraph","text":"《杜》、《平》两个戏已成熟了，可以拍片子了，但要先看一个月的戏。八一厂要出个导演。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"247b6f1f71","type":"paragraph","text":"唢呐《百鸟朝凤》可以演奏，老百姓喜欢的东西不要轻易丢掉，传统的东西不要随便去动它。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"7364f813be","type":"paragraph","text":"晚会很好，搞个录音给我。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"97dcc77da7","type":"paragraph","text":"舞蹈可拍电影。《练兵场》海洋搞成红的，没道理，怎么搞红海洋？","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"5e748607b7","type":"paragraph","text":" （文化部办公厅提供）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16"}],"page":{"id":"607b73c3a1","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a694c61e16","start":0,"end":0}},"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02a342307c","type":"paragraph","text":"弹筝的女同志不敢穿裙子，可以穿褶裙，设计几种，淡绿、淡蓝、银灰色的。","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"0b47a51e3c","type":"paragraph","text":"②看女声弹唱时说：这衣服还不错，可设计几套不同的式样，在不同的季节穿。给她们买一双白色塑料鞋也不算多嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"136027cd8f","type":"paragraph","text":"这个舞蹈整个色彩没绿，很单调。椰子树也太小，也不给点光，像个瘪三。","index":13,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"245c192266","type":"paragraph","text":"（文化部办公厅提供）","index":24,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"2a1586c225","type":"paragraph","text":"③舞蹈","index":7,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"4127527db2","type":"paragraph","text":"③朱××的裙子很难看，又短，至少可加长二寸，设计白色的，你们不敢穿，我带头穿。","index":18,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"4191cee66c","type":"paragraph","text":"④舞蹈：送粮","index":12,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"452ee461d2","type":"paragraph","text":"《霸王别姬》就可搞成一个很好的剑舞。京剧可说是集汉族歌舞精华之大成。","index":10,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"47753abc52","type":"title","text":"江青观看歌舞演出的讲话记录稿","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"a694c61e16"},{"id":"4da87a09c3","type":"paragraph","text":"听工艺展览会的同志讲，